<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: #16a34a; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .content { background: #f9fafb; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .field { margin: 10px 0; }
        .label { font-weight: bold; color: #666; }
        .value { color: #000; }
        .success { background: #dcfce7; border: 1px solid #16a34a; padding: 15px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 4px; color: #15803d; }
        .info { background: #f3f4f6; border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6; padding: 10px; margin: 15px 0; }
        .footer { text-align: center; color: #666; font-size: 12px; padding: 20px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>‚úÖ Risk Acceptance Approved</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear {{ risk_owner.firstName }} {{ risk_owner.lastName }},</p>

            <div class="success">
                <strong>‚úÖ Your risk acceptance request has been approved!</strong>
            </div>

            <div class="field">
                <span class="label">Risk Title:</span>
                <span class="value"><strong>{{ risk.title }}</strong></span>
            </div>

            <div class="field">
                <span class="label">Residual Risk Score:</span>
                <span class="value">{{ risk.residualRiskLevel }} ({{ risk.residualProbability }} √ó {{ risk.residualImpact }})</span>
            </div>

            <div class="field">
                <span class="label">Approved By:</span>
                <span class="value">{{ approver.fullName }} ({{ approver.email }})</span>
            </div>

            <div class="field">
                <span class="label">Approval Date:</span>
                <span class="value">{{ approved_at|date('d.m.Y H:i') }}</span>
            </div>

            <div class="info">
                <strong>üìã Next Steps:</strong><br>
                ‚Ä¢ The risk status has been updated to "Accepted"<br>
                ‚Ä¢ Ensure that the accepted risk is monitored according to your organization's risk review schedule<br>
                ‚Ä¢ Document this decision in your risk register for audit purposes<br>
                ‚Ä¢ Consider setting a review date to reassess this risk periodically
            </div>

            <div class="info">
                <strong>‚ÑπÔ∏è ISO 27005:2022 Compliance:</strong><br>
                This formal risk acceptance is documented in accordance with ISO 27005:2022 Section 8.4.4. The decision has been logged in the audit trail for compliance purposes.
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated notification from Little ISMS Helper</p>
            <p>ISO 27001:2022 & ISO 27005:2022 Compliant Risk Management System</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
